&lt;h1 id="part-1-install-clamav"&gt;Part 1: Install ClamAV&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id="step-1-install-clamav-and-dependencies"&gt;Step 1: Install ClamAV and Dependencies&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Update your package list and install ClamAV along with its daemon, update tool, and inotify utilities:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt update
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt install clamav clamav-daemon clamav-freshclam inotify-tools -y
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Package descriptions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>